Package: samesies
Title: Measure Similarity Across Text, Factors, or Numbers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A reliability tool for comparing the similarity of texts, factors, or numbers 
    across two or more lists. The motivating use case is to evaluate the reliability of 
    Large Language Model (LLM) responses across models, providers, or prompts.
